snippet.title: DodgeBomb Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
DodgeBomb is an intense and satisfying arcade game about dodging swarms and triggering bombs.  Wishlist it now:

https://store.steampowered.com/app/2647800/DodgeBomb/

DODGE and weave your way through massive the flood of enemies.  Lure them into range and detonate a devastating BOMB!  High Scores!  Dazzling visuals!  Epic soundscape!  Local co-op!  Dodge!  Bomb!

Coming to PC, Xbox Series S/X, and Playstation 5 in Q3 2024.
